Vendored from https://registry.npmjs.org/.

To refresh:
  npm view @xterm/xterm versions --json
  npm pack @xterm/xterm@<v> @xterm/addon-fit@<v> @xterm/addon-web-links@<v>
  tar -xzf <each>.tgz
  cp package/lib/xterm.js           src/vendor/xterm/xterm.js
  cp package/css/xterm.css          src/vendor/xterm/xterm.css
  cp package/lib/addon-fit.js       src/vendor/xterm/addon-fit.js
  cp package/lib/addon-web-links.js src/vendor/xterm/addon-web-links.js
  cp package/LICENSE                src/vendor/xterm/LICENSE

UMD bundles attach to globalThis:
  window.Terminal           — main constructor (from xterm.js)
  window.FitAddon.FitAddon  — resize-to-container helper
  window.WebLinksAddon.WebLinksAddon — clickable URL parser
